title: [Vornavian Coast, North Beach]
description: The wind decreases to a breeze as the towering cliffs approach the shoreline here.  The black sands are bathed in moonlight and stars dot the evening sky.  Grasses and small bushes sway in the breeze high atop the cliffs.

The wind decreases to a breeze as the towering cliffs approach the shoreline here.  The black sands bake so hotly in the sun that the heat can be felt even through boots.  Grasses and small bushes sway in the breeze high atop the cliffs.
